body:
@pwendell @mateiz ok I addressed those comments, and simplified things quite a bit. I removed the registry and just used `.get()` (etc) directly for the standard `Writable` types.

Also created factory method for instantiating a `Converter` and did that early on in `PythonRDD` methods.

Finally, used `RDD.first()` to check for Pickle-ability of the keys and values.
